As a Historian, I require the content of the historical document to perform the analysis.

Please provide the text content of the file named "file.txt" so I can extract the mentioned persons, places, and dates and format the output as the requested JSON object.

**Example of how I will respond once you provide the text:**

If the text was:
*"On July 20, 1789, General Lafayette, stationed near Paris, received a dispatch from King Louis XVI concerning the unrest in the city."*

My output would be:
```json
{
"persons_mentioned": ["General Lafayette", "King Louis XVI"],
"places_mentioned": ["Paris"],
"dates_mentioned": ["July 20, 1789"]
}
```
